{"lemma":"جَوْرُ","slug":"جَوْرُ","root":"ج.#.ر","root_slug":"ج-_-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-_-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["name","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4883","n5408","n6677","n6673"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَارَ (jāra) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"injustice, oppression, tyranny"},{"pos":"name","gloss":"Gōr (a former city in Fars Province, Iran; modern Firuzabad)"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Borrowed from Persian گور (Gōr)."},"ipa":["/d͡ʒawr/","/d͡ʒuːr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4883","headword_ar":"جُوّرٌ","root":"jA^r","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA^orN","text_ar":"جَاْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n5408","headword_ar":"جِوَرٌّ","root":"jr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is mentioned by Az in this art., meaning Rain"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that draws along everything:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and rain"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that occasions the herbage to grow tall:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large and heavy"},{"kind":"text","text":"[bucket of the kind called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garob","text_ar":"غَرْب"},{"kind":"text","text":"; explained in this sense by AO: and a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bulky"},{"kind":"text","text":"camel; and, with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", in like manner applied to a ewe: Fr says that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this word may be considered as augmentative or as radical. (TA.) [See also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6677","headword_ar":"جِوَرٌّ","root":"jwr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A rain"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accompanied by vehement thunder:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by a vehement sound of thunder:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"copious"},{"kind":"text","text":"rain; as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA^orN","text_ar":"جَاْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juw^arN","text_ar":"جُوَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jA^r","text_ar":"جار"},{"kind":"text","text":";) and, accord. to As,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juw^aArN","text_ar":"جُوَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and an"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exceedingly great"},{"kind":"text","text":"torrent. (TA. [In this last sense written in a copy of the A ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaworN","text_ar":"جَوْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and there said to be tropical.]) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawaArN","text_ar":"جَوَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jr","text_ar":"جر"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  You say also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAzilN jiwar~N","text_ar":"بَازِلٌ جِوَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) [app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A camel nine years old that brays loudly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard and strong:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEiyrN jiwar~N","text_ar":"بَعِيرٌ جِوَرٌّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bulky camel."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n6673","headword_ar":"جَوْرٌ","root":"jwr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", an inf. n. used as an epithet, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAy^irN","text_ar":"جَايِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Declining,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deviating, from the right course:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acting wrongfully, unjustly, injuriously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tyrannically:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl. [of the latter], applied to men, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawarapN","text_ar":"جَوَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) in which the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"remains unaltered contr. to rule, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaArapN","text_ar":"جَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,) as in all the copies of the K, but some substitute for it, as a correction, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juwarapN","text_ar":"جُوَرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [found in a copy of the A,] which, however, requires consideration, (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAy^iruwna","text_ar":"جَايِرُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TariyqN jaworN","text_ar":"طَرِيقٌ جَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A road,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"way, deviating from the right course."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa jaworN","text_ar":"هُوَ جَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano TariyqinaA","text_ar":"عَنْ طَرِيقِنَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is declining,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deviating, from our way."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  Also, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw jawor","text_ar":"ذُو جَوْر"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wronged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unjustly treated, by the judge."},{"kind":"page_break","n":484},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh from a trad.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Einodahu mina AlmaAli Aljaworu","text_ar":"عِنْدَهُ مِنَ المَالِ الجَوْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He possesses, of property, an extraordinary abundance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiwar~N","text_ar":"جِوَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["TA","K","A"]}]}}